author: @sand9282
text: The field of AI might become more restricted to computer science professionals in the future. Recent advancements in AI, coupled with growing concerns about data security and malicious viruses, could lead to stricter entry requirements.  While it's still possible to learn about AI from various backgrounds, transitioning into a technical AI role (like those involving Generative AI) may become significantly more difficult.  However, individuals with domain knowledge in finance, banking, or sales could potentially find it easier to bridge the gap into applied AI roles within their fields.
